 initial energy radiated\naway as gravitational waves. The methods developed here could be relevant for\nother problems in strong field gravity and cosmology that involve particle\ndistributions of matter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Jul 2018 20:44:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 25 Oct 2018 17:05:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-07"}
